2004-09-01  Baptiste Lepilleur  <gaiacrtn@free.fr>  [87051183eea0f573bd4f3521446d7eb4da4622be]

	Include/cppunit/XmlOutputter.

	include/cppunit/XmlOutputter.h:
	* include/cppunit/tools/XmlDocument.h
