	* contrib/readme.txt: updated.

	* contrib/bc5/bc5-makefile.zip: added borland 5.5 makefile. Contributed by
	project cuppa.

	* src/cppunit/TypeInfoHelper.cpp: fixed implementation to be more
	portable.

