2001-06-11  Baptiste Lepilleur  <gaiacrtn@free.fr>  [0c5051a8acf83fd77a6094177eb0711d3f90d997]

	Examples/cppunittest/TestResultTest.

	examples/cppunittest/TestResultTest.*: renamed TestListenerTest.*

